    "text": "Skip to content\n\n🌟 Spently is officially changing our name to UpOrder. Learn more and try it free. 🌟\nspentlyapp\nGet UpOrder Pricing Partners\nResources\nLog in\nCart\nTransactional\nEmail Templates\nfor Shopify\nUSE YOUR HIGHEST OPENED EMAILS TO DRIVE SALES\nTry UpOrder\nIncrease sales by 15% by turning your boring Shopify notification emails into a powerful post purchase customer experience.\nEASILY BRING YOUR EMAILS ON BRAND\nElevate your post purchase experience\nUnify the customer experience by providing consistent branding and visuals across in-store, online, and your customer's inbox. Spently optimizes all of your Shopify email notifications to maximize revenue with marketing content in your most opened emails.\nTry UpOrder\nDRIVE REPEAT SALES\nPowerful product recommendations\nInclude product recommendations to increase order size and drive repeat sales. Use our recommendation engine to recommend products or take control and set your own rules and conditions.\nREWARD LOYAL CUSTOMERS\nConditional discounts\nInclude personalized, one-time use discount codes and set expiration dates to generate revenue faster with urgency. Configure rules to only apply to orders above X amount, or only displays if abandoned checkout value is above X amount.\nMEASURE RESULTS\nActionable insights\nSpently is the only place to monitor your notification email performance! Easily identify your most valuable customers, highest-clicked links, revenue from Spently, in addition to opens and clicks.\nDon't take our word for it\n\nCase Studies\nView all\nFEB 15, 2021\nLearn how Assouline has driven repeat purchases for multiple stores\nFEB 15, 2021\nLearn How Hat Heaven’s transactional emails have a unique open rate of over 60% with Spently.\nFEB 15, 2021\nHow Nudestix turned emails into dollars with Spently\nRESOURCES\nHelp Center\nCase Studies\nInspiration\nTraining Webinar\nBlog\nMAIN MENU\nGet UpOrder\nPricing\nPartners\nResources\nLEGAL\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms of Service\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nLinkedIn\nYouTube\nPowered by Shopify",
